> cosa renderebbe rex un animale?
< There's more than one way: either rex is a gatto, or rex is a cane — any one would make rex a animale.
> perché rex non è un animale?
< rex is not a animale because every alternative is blocked: gatto -> animale needs rex is a gatto; cane -> animale needs rex is a cane.

